@node "Future" "Future"
@next "Thanx"
@prev "History"


What will I maybe do:

* Make DizIT work with multiple directories
* Make DizIT work faster! :)
* More filelisting 'styles' in result file
* "Definable" style of filelisting
* Include config file, for easier definition of locations for Lha,
  DmsDescript and other programs! Why do You have to call Your LhA - LhA? :)
* Include other location than RAM: for extracting! Also in config file

What I will NOT do for sure:

* Include requesters! I don't need them at all! That's why I made this one!
* Make any kind of GUI-driven DizIT! I don't need it too! And You!?
* Port it to PC! :->

